{"tid":1717400,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"關於浸大Pacific coffee被裝修，有少少意見","createTime":"2019-11-13T15:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T15:34:46.000Z","uid":191290,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3856b8c3cfb5977dec85ca64dbccff962c11f1a3","tid":1717400,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:03:53.000Z","msg":"朋友喺Pacific做part time, 今日個公司group有人提及今日裝修嘅細節：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FYnHXoX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFYnHXoX.jpg&h=60e81200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先表明立場先，呢個只係片面之詞，無圖無盛，無得fc。我唔認為一定有手足咁做或者係真手足做嘅，只係想趁機會同大家重溫一下，以下嘅三不原則。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/chrxAcK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FchrxAcK.jpg&h=1d03b480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果各位見到有藍絲廢老咁做，記住影低同喝柒佢哋。而望落似手足做緊嘢嘅，就好聲好氣咁幫手提醒下唔好咁做，互勉呀各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"a217f859e22fdd3f4c81b557df3a512b87b5f0f2","tid":1717400,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:06.000Z","msg":"自推1/3"},{"pid":"71632ba42e2afd1f4b5c36071d2801dc20d10a75","tid":1717400,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:28.000Z","msg":"自推2/3"},{"pid":"c03789f798732a1ee147a107c8b3630393c22154","tid":1717400,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"自推3/3"},{"pid":"e6f9e06872845247753091c3cd70b2e74c669aa4","tid":1717400,"uid":78349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:05:57.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"f5a3f7177bd30b6ef86c30d7bc39c77e99d2b6f8","tid":1717400,"uid":302905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T15:07:16.000Z","msg":"手足係唔會做呢啲事<br />\n我淨係信